<plot>Werner Boote presents an up-close and personal view of the controversial and fascinating material that has found its way into every facet of our daily lives: plastic. He takes us on a journey around the globe, following plastic through its 100 years of "glorious triumph" and showing us what an unexpected impact plastic has on our world.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?434873</url></doc>
